<br>
There are a lot of people who will not understand what is going on, I'm sure there are tons of pepole who browse the calendar every day and are not aware of this post.  Blakclist the raid leaders, but I would think that if you blacklist people who sign up you are hurting innocent people more than you are the guilty--if people aren't going to respect the calendar they won't need people like Harne to set up open raids for them, but 75% of the raid DOES, and they are most likely not aware that they are screwing themselves out of it.<br>
<br>
As for me, I don't really sign up for open raids anymore (Except Amori's /wink) but I have a lot of friends who are just getting to go on planars, halls of testing, a lot of fun raid areas, and I'd hate to think they get blacklisted because they are ignorant...anyway my point is if you are going to go through with this, do something to educate people besides this post, because not everyone is going to read this, and not everyone is going to understand it anyway.<br>
<br>
Flame away or whatever.<br>
<br>
