The reason why I want to place individuals versus just the raids is because even though you blacklist the raid and the raid leaders, they WILL continue to lead raids IF they have support. The less support they have, the more they will be forced to follow the rules. I'm basically undercutting them by depriving them of their ability to gather people. IF they had the manpower already, they wouldn't be using open raids. <br>
