The idea behind posting the raid is that it lets people know which raids not to honor.  So if a raid leader posts more than two weeks out, notice is sent to Lanys that their raid shouldn't be respected and anyone is well within their rights to get there first/schedule a raid there for the same day same time.<br>
<br>
Also, listing the raid/guild/raid leader instead of the participants will make for a much smaller and more maintainable list.  Either way, I agree with the previous poster that it should be stickied at the top of the forum where everyone can see it.<br>
